edictive options based on user’s input or context,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"and is commonly used to capture filtering decisions.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Suggestion chip is typically non-selected by default and can be tapped or clicked to apply the suggestion, streamlining input and enhancing usability.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Chips can show multiple interactive elements together in the same area, such as a list of selectable movie times, or a serie of email contacts.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Best suited for category-based filters that do not require additional visual elements.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSuggestionChip"},"doc://OUDSThemesContract/documentation/OUDSThemesContract/OUDSTheme":{"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OUDSTheme","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemescontract\/oudstheme","role":"symbol","type":"topic","title":"OUDSTheme","fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSTheme","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"text":"This is a basic theme any theme must be a subclass off, or all themes must have as ancestor.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"A Swift ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"class"},{"text":" has been used so as to allow to easily override some attributes and have inheritance, without having for developers","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to implement all tokens.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Any properties of an overridable theme should be defined so as to provide defaults values.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"We allow this theme to be derivated and be overriden.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/OUDSTheme","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" can be seen as a kind of “abstract class” in ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"object oriented paradigm","type":"text"}]},{"text":", or ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"theme contract","type":"text"}]},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Because ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"text":" is not a ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"final","type":"text"}]},{"text":" class, its type cannot be seen as ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Sendable"},{"text":", that is the reason why this conformity is unchecked.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/OUDSTheme","kind":"symbol"}}}